100864::g_decay_a::The sage cries out.	"Open, Gates of Heaven. Bless us and bestow miracles upon us!"	The sage cries out in regret.	"Close, Gates of Heaven. Save us from all our sins and evil!"::
100865::g_decay_b::The curtain closes.	The millennium comes to a standstill.	Our dreams, our hopes... were a forbidden "failure" from the start.::
100866::g_decay_c::The stars fall out of the sky.	Space closes up into nothingness.	The pathway to the center is shrouded along with our sins.		...I am, at last, filled with joy.::
100867::g_decay_d::All has been engulfed by darkness.	Nothing can hurt you now.	At least, you have been set free from the pain that you carried for so long.		You may now rest, without a worry on your mind.::
100873::g_rinmemo::After school. Behind the range. In the grove.	 I'm not mad about this morning, so come.	If you don't come, I'll kill you go home.::
100874::g_epologue::epilogue.::
