101373::g_tigercaution::Tiger Dojo is a light-hearted hint segment.	Players who want to complete the game on their own or	avoid out-of-character situations should proceed with caution.::
101374::g_letext001::"I'm back, Saber."::
101375::title00_17::REMASTERED::
