101392::g_saed_font01-1::The battle is over.::
101393::g_saed_font01-2::Let us put our swords down, and rest in the momentary peace.::
101394::g_saed_font01-3::After dozing in a warm dream, a new day will dawn.::
101395::g_saed_font01-4::The days continue on...::
101396::g_saed_font01-5::And we are still following the same star we once saw.::
101397::g_sked_font01-1::Winter has gone, and spring has come.::
101398::g_sked_font01-2::Nature is in its full bloom, and there is nothing left that reminds you of::
101399::g_sked_font01-3::the hard cold days.::
101400::g_sked_font01-4::Stash away both what you lost and gained, for life continues on.::
101401::g_sked_font01-5::Now then...::
101402::g_sked_font01-6::The story that unraveled in this town has reached its conclusion.::
101403::g_sked_font01-7::New stages and people await us...::
101404::g_rned_font01-1::Walk with the wind in your face.::
101405::g_rned_font01-2::Walk towards the future.::
101406::g_rned_font01-3::Live busy days with no compass to guide you.::
101407::g_rned_font01-4::After traveling to distant exotic countries...::
101408::g_rned_font01-5::You will return to where you belong, one sunny day.::

